{"tid":1223892,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"80幾萬撐送中既入一入黎 睇下日本反送中既集會","createTime":"2019-06-14T23:09:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-15T00:13:37.000Z","uid":75156,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4e31e5fcaf6f5c08cd2eb0ad812dd23c56fbbb39","tid":1223892,"uid":75156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T23:09:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/d9vc8nYuAUM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fd9vc8nYuAUM&d=YB8lrFeyQ%2BkzHCEHpdql8EVeFFKYYtZMgzuY3n553xQ%3D&h=2a06067d\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/d9vc8nYuAUM</a><br />\n屌你老味 日本仔支持香港反送中既都多過你地呀<br />\n日撚日就個廿幾個出黎話唔要逃犯天堂<br />\n仲有幾個老臨黎 反醒下啦 <br />\n日本個班唔係日本華僑黎架 係日本人<br />\n支持行動都實際過你班撚樣<br />\n仲撐送中個班真不知所謂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n幾萬蚊做下樣就算<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14009e56d3bbc01c57acb620f07641b7d4661ae8","tid":1223892,"uid":75156,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T23:11:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aFY98E4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaFY98E4.png&h=38ca50e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁唔鍾意睇到反送中集會<br />\n派人過去清場呀笨 濕鳩政府"},{"pid":"9cfc1cc3ca682be7022ad501021c6e64f5afa652","tid":1223892,"uid":1678,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T23:15:14.000Z","msg":"一半在日港人黎<br />\n但個活動搞手鬼鬼地 同日本共產黨有關"},{"pid":"5f5a54c23de5655469cfe57215603b49cbaf182c","tid":1223892,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9cfc1cc3ca682be7022ad501021c6e64f5afa652","tid":1223892,"uid":1678,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T23:15:14.000Z","msg":"一半在日港人黎<br />\n但個活動搞手鬼鬼地 同日本共產黨有關"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T23:18:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"daf08ecf3e82c5a7843f7cc38e82414b38f6dcf4